---
import flag from "../../assets/images/Burners/flag.svg";
import PlaCQuemador from '../../assets/images/Burners/PlaC Quemador.webp'
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section class="w-full font-bold text-black mt-20 flex flex-col gap-10">
  <div class="w-full bg-[url(/newBanner.webp)] px-8 lg:px-52 py-20">
    <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
      <Image src={flag} alt="Flag icon" class="w-[150px] md:w-[200px]" />
    </div>
    <p class="text-white font-bold text-base lg:text-xl">
      Our latest burner innovation features an oxygen sensor that automatically
      regulates excess oxygen to no more than 3%, eliminating the need for
      manual fuel carburization adjustment when relocating the equipment. Thanks
      to our self-carburizing system, NOx levels remain even lower.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="space-y-3">
    <div class="w-1/5 h-[2px] bg-redBg"></div>
    <div class="w-1/6 h-[2px] bg-blueMain"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="w-full max-w-7xl px-8 mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl">
      Choose the Fuel, We'll Handle the Performance
    </h2><br />
    <p class="text-sm md:text-xl">
      We understand the importance of fuel versatility for efficient operation.
      Our burners are designed to support multiple fuel types, giving you the
      flexibility to select the option that best suits your process.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div
    class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-2 md:gap-10 max-w-7xl px-8 mx-auto justify-center items-center"
  >
    <div class="flex justify-center w-full">
      <div
        class="w-3/4 bg-white rounded-2xl p-4 flex flex-col gap-4 justify-center"
      >
        <h2 class="text-center text-xl md:text-2xl">Natural Gas</h2>
        <div class="w-full h-[2px] bg-redBg"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center w-full">
      <div class="w-3/4 bg-white rounded-2xl p-4 flex flex-col gap-4">
        <h2 class="text-center text-xl md:text-2xl">
          Liquefied Petroleum Gas (LPG)
        </h2>
        <div class="w-full h-[2px] bg-redBg"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center w-full">
      <div class="w-3/4 bg-white rounded-2xl p-4 flex flex-col gap-4">
        <h2 class="text-center text-xl md:text-2xl">Alternative Fuels</h2>
        <div class="w-full h-[2px] bg-blueMain"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center w-full">
      <div class="w-3/4 bg-white rounded-2xl p-4 flex flex-col gap-4">
        <h2 class="text-center text-xl md:text-2xl">Diesel</h2>
        <div class="w-full h-[2px] bg-blueMain"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex mx-auto max-w-7xl justify-end">
    <Image src={PlaCQuemador} alt="Aggregate Drying Plant" class="w-4/5 md:w-1/2" />
  </div>
</section>
